# Student Performance Analysis

## Project Overview

This project analyzes student performance data using Power BI. The objective is to identify patterns and factors affecting academic performance through interactive visualizations and dashboards.

## Dataset Information

The dataset includes:

* Gender
* Race/Ethnicity
* Parental Level of Education
* Test Preparation Course
* Math Score
* Reading Score
* Writing Score

## Project Objectives

* Analyze student academic performance
* Compare scores across different groups
* Identify factors influencing performance
* Create interactive visualizations and dashboards
* Generate meaningful insights from the data

## Dashboard Features

* Student Count
* Average Math Score
* Average Reading Score
* Average Writing Score
* Gender-wise Analysis
* Ethnicity-wise Analysis
* Parental Education Analysis
* Test Preparation Course Analysis
* Interactive Filters (Slicers)

## Tools Used

* Power BI Desktop
* CSV Dataset
* Microsoft Word
* GitHub

## Key Insights

* Student performance varies across different demographic groups.
* Test preparation courses can positively influence performance.
* Parental education level shows a relationship with student achievement.
* Interactive dashboards help in understanding performance trends effectively.

## Files Included

* Student_Performance_Analysis.pbix
* StudentsPerformance.csv
* Student_Performance_Analysis_Report.pdf
* Dashboard Screenshot

